# rpcUnsuccessful

**Type Property**

The structure of the remote procedure call (RPC) is bad.

## Declaration

```swift
static var rpcUnsuccessful: Errno { get }
```

## Discussion

Exchange of RPC information was unsuccessful.

The corresponding C error is `EBADRPC`.

## RPC Errors

- **rpcProcedureUnavailable**: Bad procedure for program.
- **rpcProgramUnavailable**: The remote procedure call (RPC) program isn’t available.
- **rpcProgramVersionMismatch**: The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) program is incorrect.
- **rpcVersionMismatch**: The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) is incorrect.
